==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: glued
<hw>glued</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>affixed with glue or
paste.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pasted, stuck to(predicate).</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>having the attention so concentrated as to be
difficult to cause a person to leave; <as>as, <ex>glued</ex> to the
television set; The audience was <ex>glued</ex> to their
seats</as>.</def> <mark>[metaphorical]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> riveted.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gluepot</ent>⟦br⟧
